 {"id":"bd-2n73","title":"Gateway + private sync with ACFS/tooling vNext","description":"Objective: align Flywheel Gateway (public) and flywheel_private (private) with the latest ACFS manifest v2 and the expanded Dicklesworthstone tool ecosystem. Incorporate new tools/utilities, updated robot/JSON/TOON interfaces, and ACFS manifest-driven metadata so the dashboard, APIs, and detection logic match the real installed stack. Constraints: keep business-sensitive configs in /dp/flywheel_private; avoid leaking private data into public repo. Success: Gateway presents accurate tool inventory/health, supports new tool APIs, and private repo holds sensitive configs/overrides.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:05.828388561Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:05.828388561Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
 {"id":"bd-2n73.1","title":"Tooling delta audit (ACFS manifest + /dp tool repos)","description":"Survey ACFS manifest v2 and each tool repo in /dp to produce a canonical delta list: new tools, renamed commands, new robot flags/output formats (JSON/JSONL/TOON), new MCP servers, and changed install/verify semantics. Map each tool to existing gateway integration (service, route, UI) and mark gaps. Deliverable: a structured matrix (tool → CLI → robot/mcp → gateway support status) to drive implementation beads.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:14.981930324Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T19:43:43.767053327Z","closed_at":"2026-01-27T19:43:43.766195611Z","close_reason":"Completed comprehensive tooling delta audit v2. Document at docs/tooling-delta-audit-v2.md covers 16 tools, identifies gaps, and provides actionable items for downstream beads.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.1","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:14.981930324Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
 {"id":"bd-2n73.10","title":"Web UI: utilities workflows (giil/csctf/xf/etc)","description":"Add/expand utilities UI flows for new tools: giil image fetch, csctf transcript export, xf archive search, toon viewer, and related helper UIs. Ensure inputs/outputs map to new gateway endpoints and include clear logging of tool outputs. Add UI tests to validate form validation, error states, and result rendering. Success: operators can run these utilities from the dashboard without using the CLI directly.","status":"open","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:38:21.495466158Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T19:26:26.113142813Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.10","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:38:21.495466158Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.10","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.11","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:42:36.206977166Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.10","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:42:22.084703559Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
