 {"id":"bd-2n73.12","title":"flywheel_private: secrets/config for new tools","description":"In /dp/flywheel_private, add/update private configuration for new tools (tokens, API keys, credential files, account rotation metadata). Provide secure loading hooks for gateway so public repo never stores sensitive data. Success: private repo contains all sensitive tool configuration with documented loading points.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:38:33.460508536Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T18:42:58.615481086Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.12","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:38:33.460508536Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.12","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:42:58.615328749Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
