+{"id":"bd-2n73.3","title":"Tool detection vNext (manifest-driven + new CLIs)","description":"Upgrade agent/tool detection to use ACFS manifest and cover new CLIs/utilities (ms, wa, pt, rch, giil, csctf, xf, toon, rano, mdwb, s2p, rust_proxy, aadc, caam, slb, dcg, ubs, etc.). Include version, auth, robot capability checks, and explicit detection of MCP servers. Add deterministic test fixtures for PATH probing and auth/permission errors. Success: /agents/detected returns full, accurate tool inventory for the current machine.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:28.136243746Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T22:21:33.196382481Z","closed_at":"2026-01-27T22:21:33.196294936Z","close_reason":"Completed tool detection vNext:\n- Expanded FALLBACK_TOOL_CLIS with 11 new tools (slb, ms, xf, pt, rch, giil, csctf, caam, ntm, scanner + already had dcg/ubs/cass/cm/br/bv/ru)\n- Added RobotModeInfo interface with supported, flag, outputFormats, envelopeCompliant fields\n- Added McpInfo interface with available, capabilities, toolCount fields\n- Extended DetectedCapabilities to include robotMode and mcp\n- Updated deriveCapabilities to extract robot mode and MCP from manifest\n- Added comprehensive test fixtures for agent-detection.service.ts (27 tests covering PATH probing, auth errors, robot mode detection, MCP detection)","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:28.136243746Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:39:53.600533426Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.2","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:39:34.107278206Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2n73.3","depends_on_id":"bd-2n73.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:39:43.801395043Z","created